1. Hind Rajab - Age 6
   Detail: Trapped in car in Tel al-Hawa, Gaza City on January 29, 2024. Called emergency services. Two paramedics were also killed trying to reach her.
   Source:

2. Yazan Al-Kafarneh - Age 10
   Detail: Died of starvation in Kamal Adwan Hospital, northern Gaza, January 2024. Weighed less than 15kg at death.
   Source:

3. Reem Al-Najjar - Age 4
   Detail: Killed in Rafah with siblings. Had just learned to ride her brother's bicycle. Mother had sewn her name in her coat collar.
   Source:

4. Mohammed Abu Daqqa - Age 12
   Detail: Lived in Khan Younis, played football daily. Coach said he was extremely fast. Killed near his home.
   Source:

5. Saly Mustafa - Age 7
   Detail: Brought to hospital conscious, asked for water and her mother (who was also killed in the strike). Died before staff answered.
   Source:

6. Lama Al-Qasim - Age 3
   Detail: Killed with mother and grandmother. Described as making everyone smile. Had recently learned to write the letter "ل" (lam).
   Source:

7. Ahmad Al-Ashqar - Age 8
   Detail: Best student in class. Drew animals in worksheet margins (dogs, birds, camels, cats). Wanted to be a veterinarian.
   Source:

8. Nour Ashour - Age 5
   Detail: Killed in Jabalia, November 2023. Parents told her loud sounds were thunder and they were camping.
   Source:

9. Ibrahim Al-Harazin - Age 11
   Detail: Documented by Euro-Med Human Rights Monitor. Wanted to be a surgeon "because surgeons fix the things that are most broken." Sixth grade student.
   Source:

10. Dina Al-Najjar - Age 9
    Detail: Killed November 2023. Mother said she "kept us smiling." Younger brother present at death and has not spoken since.
    Source:

11. Walid Hassan - Age 7
    Detail: Loved watermelon (refused to eat the white part). Would watch same cartoons repeatedly. Killed while sleeping.
    Source:

12. Farah Al-Masri - Age 13
    Detail: Was preparing for end-of-year exams. Notebooks recovered with color-coded revision notes. Lent a pen to classmate morning of strike.
    Source:

13. Omar Fathi Salameh - Age 9
    Detail: Known for memorizing Quran passages. Habit of finishing sentences just before imam during prayers. Killed with four cousins.
    Source:

14. A child whose name was not recorded - Age unknown
    Detail: Represents thousands of unidentified children beneath rubble whose names were known to someone but not documented.
    Source:
